```mermaid
graph TD
    Client["🌐 Client (Web / Mobile)"]

    Client --> GW

    subgraph Gateway Layer
        GW[API Gateway]
    end

    GW --> AUTH
    GW --> USER
    GW --> RIDE
    GW --> PAY
    GW --> NOTIF
    GW --> TRACK
    GW --> ANALYTICS
    GW --> REVIEW

    subgraph Core Services
        AUTH[Auth Service]
        USER[User Service]
        RIDE[Ride Service]
        PAY[Payment Service]
        NOTIF[Notification Service]
        TRACK[Tracking Service]
        ANALYTICS[Analytics Service]
        REVIEW[Review & Rating Service]
    end

    AUTH --> AUTH_DB[(Auth DB\nPostgreSQL)]
    USER --> USER_DB[(User DB\nPostgreSQL)]
    RIDE --> RIDE_DB[(Ride DB\nMongoDB)]
    PAY --> PAY_DB[(Payment DB\nPostgreSQL)]
    REVIEW --> REVIEW_DB[(Review DB\nMongoDB)]
    ANALYTICS --> ANALYTICS_DB[(Analytics DB\nClickHouse)]
    TRACK --> CACHE[(Location Cache\nRedis)]

    RIDE -->|ride booked event| MQ
    PAY -->|payment event| MQ
    REVIEW -->|review event| MQ
    TRACK -->|location update| MQ

    subgraph Message Broker
        MQ[Message Queue\nRabbitMQ / Kafka]
    end

    MQ --> NOTIF
    MQ --> ANALYTICS
    MQ --> USER

    PAY --> EXT_PAY[External Payment\nGateway]
    NOTIF --> EXT_EMAIL[Email Provider\nSendGrid]
    NOTIF --> EXT_SMS[SMS Provider\nTwilio]
```
